WEBVTT

00:00.935 --> 00:02.179
Look at this girl!

00:03.319 --> 00:05.331
She is so cute and lovely.

00:06.503 --> 00:08.171
She wears a red cloak.

00:09.373 --> 00:11.849
Her name is Little Red Riding Hood.

00:13.073 --> 00:14.772
Little Red Riding Hood!

00:16.093 --> 00:16.999
Yes, mom!

00:18.230 --> 00:21.756
Your grandma is ill. Carry this cake to her.

00:22.951 --> 00:23.882
Yes, mom!

00:25.197 --> 00:28.734
On the way, Little Red Riding Hood meets a wolf.

00:30.039 --> 00:32.460
She looks yummy!

00:33.703 --> 00:37.239
Hi! Where are you going?

00:38.572 --> 00:42.307
I'm going to see my grandma. She is sick.

00:43.527 --> 00:46.653
Where does your grandma live?

00:47.864 --> 00:51.011
Over there, the first house in the village.

